.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE_PAY_FEE_SKEWNESS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-pay-fee-skewness \- FEAT-2814 skewness of payment fees
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-pay-fee-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the skewness of payment fees for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2814).
.PP
Output: JSON object with key \fBfee_skewness_pay\fR and \fBcount\fR.
Returns \fBnull\fR when fewer than the required minimum samples are available.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning (1)
